author: Al Jazeera
title: Wisconsin Republican legislators sue to block stay-at-home orders
description: Wisconsin and other US states have seen a string of protests against measures aimed at containing the coronavirus.
content:
Wisconsin's Republican-controlled state legislature on Tuesday took to the courts in an attempt to force health officials in that state to rescind an extended stay-at-home order intended to curb the coronavirus pandemic.
